---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Contact — BCC"
  description="Get in touch with the BCC team to report incorrect color data, suggest a new team, or ask a general question."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">BCC</a> <span>›</span> <span>Contact</span></div>
      <h1>Contact</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Report incorrect color data, suggest a missing team, or just say hello.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-section">
        <p class="section-label">Send a message</p>
        <form class="form" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="subject">Subject</label>
            <select id="subject" name="subject">
              <option value="color-correction">Incorrect color data</option>
              <option value="missing-team">Missing team</option>
              <option value="general">General question</option>
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Describe what you'd like to report or ask..." required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <p class="section-label">Common questions</p>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Where does the color data come from?</summary>
          <p>Colors are sourced from official team brand guidelines, style guides, and SVG logo files. Each entry includes a sourcing note explaining where the values were confirmed.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do I report an incorrect color?</summary>
          <p>Use the form above with the "Incorrect color data" subject. Please include the team name, the incorrect value, and a link to an official source confirming the correct value.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can you add a team that isn't listed?</summary>
          <p>Yes — select "Missing team" in the form and include the team name and league. We'll add it when we can verify the official color values.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 3rem 2rem 2.5rem;
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--text-accent); }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .main {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card-section {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  input, select, textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 9px 12px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color .12s;
    width: 100%;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--bg-accent);
  }

  .submit-btn {
    align-self: flex-start;
    padding: 9px 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--text-primary);
    color: var(--surface-2);
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity .12s;
  }

  .submit-btn:hover { opacity: .8; }

  .faq { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  summary {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

  summary::after {
    content: '+';
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  details[open] summary::after { content: '−'; }

  .faq-item p {
    padding: 0 16px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
</style>
